examples.en: This is the snowiest winter in years.
They slid down the snowy hill on their bellies.
Tom was inseparable from his dog, Snowy.
The children coasted on sleds down the snowy hill.
The polar bear is an iconic denizen of the snowy Arctic.
Below were the silvery lakes, above were the snowy peaks.
A snowy white stallion piaffed its hoofs to Bizet's Habanera.
